	height=&#34;1025&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95_hu18088525332516761614.png 480w, https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95_hu3282026408244610341.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;WordPress.com注册登录&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;221&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;531px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2245&#34;
	height=&#34;1098&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9_hu17778979640797537765.png 480w, https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9_hu3846005311833486312.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;域名选择&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;204&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;490px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1726&#34;
	height=&#34;1305&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF_hu4353476169839284490.png 480w, https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF_hu17301799892362240411.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;工作面板&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;132&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;317px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;注意，此时其实还没有正式进入到博客装修阶段，需要选择站点发布再次确认域名套餐，才算网站建立。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%82%AC%E4%BF%83%E7%BC%B4%E8%B4%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;804&#34;
	height=&#34;294&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%82%AC%E4%BF%83%E7%BC%B4%E8%B4%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1_hu17233023243082313050.png 480w, https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E5%82%AC%E4%BF%83%E7%BC%B4%E8%B4%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1_hu12771474469523848083.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;催促缴费警告一次&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;273&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;656px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;三番五次确认之后再度回到主页小房子界面，这个时候才能修改主题，也正式进入到博客装修环节。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2458&#34;
	height=&#34;1250&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98_hu349619196137973066.png 480w, https://retreatafter.github.io/p/blogbuildwp02/2026__%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2__%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86__WordPress%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA.%E7%AC%AC2%E9%9B%86.%E4%BB%AA%E8%A1%A8%E7%9B%98_hu16488409207058812441.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;仪表盘&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;196&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;471px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然而WordPress.com商业版的博客装修其实没多少能说的，主要原因是免费版限制了尤其多的功能——高情商说法是“我们已经为您搭建了完整的博客您只需要将ABCDE几处修改文本就可以体验使用博客了”，几乎只能使用原原本本的主题模板，想要进一步修改都会被提示是收费功能，而插件功能也是都需要付费套餐才能使用否则只会默认安装几个安全性功能的插件，而博客搭建与装修有趣（和折磨）的基本上也是这两个部分，也就是说在WordPress.com免费套餐里你是几乎对所有事情都无能为力的，对于想免费体验搭建博客过程的用户来说或许也没有那么便利……但对于对博客装修无欲无求只是想快速有一个个人页面的用户来说，也不失一个选择吧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
